title: 35+ minute Queue's
body:
This is just today i have not been able to get into a match. i didn't even realize until i swapped my window back to the launcher that i was queue for this long. to top it off i have been trying to get into a game for last two hours. i stopped queue  reset it;  relaunched the launcher. 
_**HELP**_

replies.body: What are you queuing up for?  That's really odd, and it sounds like you may have lost connection or sync from the matchmaking service.  Instead of re-queueing, I instead suggest relogging from the entire client.  Let me know if that helps.
I am currently having this same issue here if anyone knows whats going on or has an idea please notify me.
